title: Virginia Tech dives back into midweek action at VMI - VT hokiesports.com
content: Virginia Tech dives back into midweek action at VMI  VT hokiesports.com
description: Diving back into midweek action, the Virginia Tech baseball team (14-6) will look to string back-to-back victories together against in-state opposition on Tuesday, March 29, when Tech travels to VMI (8-15) for an evening affair at Gray-Minor Stadium in Lexington.
